  {"slug":"aurora-flow-background","title":"Aurora Flow","description":"Ein sanft fließender Aurora-Verlauf aus Violett, Fuchsia und Cyan, der wie Polarlichter über einen dunklen Nachthimmel wandert und dabei GPU-schonend nur Transform und Opacity animiert.","framework":"css","tags":["aurora","gradient","dark","glow","animated"],"html":"&lt;div class=\"aurora-bg\"&gt;\n  &lt;div class=\"aurora-layer aurora-1\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div class=\"aurora-layer aurora-2\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div class=\"aurora-layer aurora-3\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;","css":".aurora-bg {\n  position: relative;\n  width: 100%;\n  max-width: 320px;\n  height: 180px;\n  border-radius: 16px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  background: #0a0a12;\n}\n.aurora-layer {\n  position: absolute;\n  width: 200%;\n  height: 200%;\n  top: -50%;\n  left: -50%;\n  border-radius: 45%;\n  filter: blur(30px);\n  opacity: 0.55;\n  will-change: transform;\n}\n.aurora-1 {\n  background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 40%, #8b5cf6, transparent 60%);\n  animation: aurora-spin-a 12s linear infinite;\n}\n.aurora-2 {\n  background: radial-gradient(circle at 70% 60%, #d946ef, transparent 60%);\n  animation: aurora-spin-b 16s linear infinite;\n}\n.aurora-3 {\n  background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, #06b6d4, transparent 55%);\n  animation: aurora-spin-a 20s linear infinite reverse;\n}\n@keyframes aurora-spin-a {\n  from { transform: rotate(0deg) translateX(6%); }\n  to { transform: rotate(360deg) translateX(6%); }\n}\n@keyframes aurora-spin-b {\n  from { transform: rotate(0deg) translateX(-8%); }\n  to { transform: rotate(-360deg) translateX(-8%); }\n}\n@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {\n  .aurora-layer { animation: none; }\n}","js":""},
  {"slug":"mesh-gradient-morph","title":"Mesh Gradient Morph","description":"Ein animierter Mesh-Gradient, bei dem mehrere farbige Lichtpunkte in Violett, Fuchsia und Cyan sanft ihre Position wechseln und so einen lebendig morphenden Farbverlauf im Dark-Theme erzeugen.","framework":"css","tags":["mesh","gradient","morph","dark","colorful"],"html":"&lt;div class=\"mesh-bg\"&gt;\n  &lt;span class=\"mesh-dot mesh-a\"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\n  &lt;span class=\"mesh-dot mesh-b\"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\n  &lt;span class=\"mesh-dot mesh-c\"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\n  &lt;span class=\"mesh-dot mesh-d\"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;","css":".mesh-bg {\n  position: relative;\n  width: 100%;\n  max-width: 320px;\n  height: 180px;\n  border-radius: 16px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  background: #0b0710;\n}\n.mesh-dot {\n  position: absolute;\n  width: 160px;\n  height: 160px;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  filter: blur(38px);\n  opacity: 0.7;\n  will-change: transform;\n}\n.mesh-a { background: #8b5cf6; top: -30px; left: -20px; animation: mesh-move-a 14s ease-in-out infinite; }\n.mesh-b { background: #d946ef; bottom: -40px; right: -20px; animation: mesh-move-b 18s ease-in-out infinite; }\n.mesh-c { background: #06b6d4; top: 20px; right: -30px; animation: mesh-move-c 16s ease-in-out infinite; }\n.mesh-d { background: #10b981; bottom: -30px; left: 20px; animation: mesh-move-a 20s ease-in-out infinite reverse; }\n@keyframes mesh-move-a {\n  0%,100% { transform: translate(0,0); }\n  50% { transform: translate(40px, 30px); }\n}\n@keyframes mesh-move-b {\n  0%,100% { transform: translate(0,0); }\n  50% { transform: translate(-45px, -25px); }\n}\n@keyframes mesh-move-c {\n  0%,100% { transform: translate(0,0); }\n  50% { transform: translate(-30px, 40px); }\n}\n@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {\n  .mesh-dot { animation: none; }\n}","js":""},
  {"slug":"neon-grid-pulse","title":"Neon Grid Pulse","description":"Ein leuchtendes Neon-Raster mit perspektivischer Tiefe, das im Rhythmus nach oben scrollt und dabei in Cyan und Violett pulsiert, um einen futuristischen Synthwave-Look im Dark-Theme zu erzeugen.","framework":"css","tags":["grid","neon","synthwave","dark","retro"],"html":"&lt;div class=\"grid-bg\"&gt;\n  &lt;div class=\"grid-plane\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div class=\"grid-glow\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;","css":".grid-bg {\n  position: relative;\n  width: 100%;\n  max-width: 320px;\n  height: 180px;\n  border-radius: 16px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0715 0%, #130a24 100%);\n  perspective: 200px;\n}\n.grid-plane {\n  position: absolute;\n  left: -50%;\n  top: 40%;\n  width: 200%;\n  height: 160%;\n  background-image:\n    linear-gradient(#8b5cf6 1px, transparent 1px),\n    linear-gradient(90deg, #06b6d4 1px, transparent 1px);\n  background-size: 32px 32px;\n  transform: rotateX(70deg);\n  transform-origin: top center;\n  opacity: 0.55;\n  animation: grid-scroll 4s linear infinite;\n  will-change: background-position;\n}\n.grid-glow {\n  position: absolute;\n  inset: 0;\n  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 60%, rgba(217,70,239,0.35), transparent 60%);\n  animation: grid-pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;\n}\n@keyframes grid-scroll {\n  from { background-position: 0 0; }\n  to { background-position: 0 32px; }\n}\n@keyframes grid-pulse {\n  0%,100% { opacity: 0.5; }\n  50% { opacity: 0.9; }\n}\n@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {\n  .grid-plane, .grid-glow { animation: none; }\n}","js":""},
  {"slug":"starfield-drift","title":"Starfield Drift","description":"Ein ruhiges Sternenfeld aus reinen CSS-Partikeln, das in mehreren Ebenen langsam nach oben driftet und mit sanft funkelnden Lichtpunkten in Weiß und Cyan eine tiefe Weltraum-Atmosphäre schafft.","framework":"css","tags":["stars","particles","space","dark","twinkle"],"html":"&lt;div class=\"star-bg\"&gt;\n  &lt;div class=\"star-layer star-far\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;div class=\"star-layer star-near\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;","css":".star-bg {\n  position: relative;\n  width: 100%;\n  max-width: 320px;\n  height: 180px;\n  border-radius: 16px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 30%, #16122b 0%, #06040d 100%);\n}\n.star-layer {\n  position: absolute;\n  top: 0;\n  left: 0;\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 200%;\n  will-change: transform;\n}\n.star-far {\n  background-image:\n    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 20px 30px, #ffffff, transparent),\n    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 80px 90px, #06b6d4, transparent),\n    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 140px 50px, #ffffff, transparent),\n    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 200px 120px, #8b5cf6, transparent),\n    radial-gradient(1px 1px at 260px 70px, #ffffff, transparent);\n  background-size: 300px 150px;\n  animation: star-drift 30s linear infinite, star-twinkle 4s ease-in-out infinite;\n}\n.star-near {\n  background-image:\n    radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 50px 60px, #ffffff, transparent),\n    radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 120px 20px, #d946ef, transparent),\n    radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 180px 100px, #ffffff, transparent),\n    radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 240px 40px, #06b6d4, transparent);\n  background-size: 300px 180px;\n  animation: star-drift 18s linear infinite, star-twinkle 3s ease-in-out infinite;\n}\n@keyframes star-drift {\n  from { transform: translateY(0); }\n  to { transform: translateY(-50%); }\n}\n@keyframes star-twinkle {\n  0%,100% { opacity: 0.5; }\n  50% { opacity: 1; }\n}\n@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {\n  .star-layer { animation: none; }\n}","js":""},
  {"slug":"floating-blobs-glow","title":"Floating Blobs Glow","description":"Weich leuchtende Gradient-Blobs in Fuchsia, Violett und Erfolgsgrün, die organisch durch den dunklen Raum schweben und dabei ihre Form leicht verändern, um eine beruhigende, moderne Tiefe zu erzeugen.","framework":"css","tags":["blobs","glow","floating","dark","organic"],"html":"&lt;div class=\"blob-bg\"&gt;\n  &lt;span class=\"blob blob-1\"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\n  &lt;span class=\"blob blob-2\"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\n  &lt;span class=\"blob blob-3\"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;","css":".blob-bg {\n  position: relative;\n  width: 100%;\n  max-width: 320px;\n  height: 180px;\n  border-radius: 16px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  background: #08060f;\n}\n.blob {\n  position: absolute;\n  width: 120px;\n  height: 120px;\n  border-radius: 42% 58% 63% 37% / 41% 44% 56% 59%;\n  filter: blur(24px);\n  opacity: 0.65;\n  will-change: transform;\n}\n.blob-1 {\n  background: #d946ef;\n  top: 10px;\n  left: 10px;\n  animation: blob-float-1 13s ease-in-out infinite;\n}\n.blob-2 {\n  background: #8b5cf6;\n  bottom: -10px;\n  right: 20px;\n  animation: blob-float-2 17s ease-in-out infinite;\n}\n.blob-3 {\n  background: #10b981;\n  top: 40px;\n  right: -10px;\n  animation: blob-float-1 21s ease-in-out infinite reverse;\n}\n@keyframes blob-float-1 {\n  0%,100% { transform: translate(0,0) scale(1); }\n  33% { transform: translate(30px, 20px) scale(1.1); }\n  66% { transform: translate(-20px, 30px) scale(0.95); }\n}\n@keyframes blob-float-2 {\n  0%,100% { transform: translate(0,0) scale(1); }\n  50% { transform: translate(-35px, -25px) scale(1.15); }\n}\n@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {\n  .blob { animation: none; }\n}","js":""}
